102
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:56,916
Mounted the machine gun on a forklift.

103
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,875
He put us all in danger.
They had to take him out.

104
00:06:59,958 --> 00:07:03,083
He had no pulse for a few minutes,
