What am I doing here?

125
00:08:10,333 --> 00:08:12,958
I'm shooting people
while my kid is with some monks.

126
00:08:14,041 --> 00:08:15,291
[cries] When he's older...

127
00:08:16,791 --> 00:08:19,666
