When the Viking gold museum opens.

171
00:10:55,708 --> 00:10:59,458
But by then,
who's gonna connect the dots? [laughs]

172
00:10:59,541 --> 00:11:00,958
- Viking gold?
- [Berlin] Mm-hmm.

173
